---
title: Curried Veggie Filo Parcels with Cucumber Salad & Minty Garlic Dip
description: These crispy parcels are like your own personal handheld pie! Flaky filo has been wrapped around a flavour-packed filling of hearty veggies with pops of sweetcorn for ultimate satisfaction. Served with a refreshing cucumber salad and a tangy garlic dip, this combo might be our new favourite!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
